{"title":"Classified 1x Crankset, Aero Chainrings & More Cassettes Fill Out their Alt 2x Drivetrain","link":"https://bikerumor.com/classified-powershift-portfolio-adds-1x-cranks-chainrings-and-more/","date":1736871209000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-30mm-carbon-crankset_pro-only-purple-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"Classified Powershift ecosystem adds direct mount crankset aero chainrings and more wide-range 12sp 13sp cassettes, purple pro\" /></p>\n<p>The Classified specialty is of course their unique 2-speed hub. But this new expanded collection of a 1x crankset, aerodynamic chainrings, and expanded cassette options may be just the thing to help more riders adopt their virtual 2x drivetrain. The aero &amp; simplicity benefits of 1x with the smooth gearing steps of 2x, with a more complete Classified solution…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Classified Powershift adds 1x cranks, chainrings &amp; more!</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Classified Powershift ecosystem adds direct mount crankset aero chainrings and more wide-range 12sp 13sp cassettes, ecosystem\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(Photos/Classified)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Classified says their new cranks and chainrings were developed to “<em>seamlessly expand our ecosystem, offering even greater compatibility and integration.</em>” Since many aftermarket adopters of the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=Classified+Powershift\" target=\"_blank\">Classified Powershift</a> 2-speed internally geared hub system are moving away from conventional 2x drivetrains, they already need to find 1x crankset alternative. Keeping it within their ecosystem helps Classified strengthen their Powershift drivetrain brand. And they aim to offer a lightweight premium carbon 1x crankset solution cheaper than most other premium setups.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1x Aero Crankset details</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-30mm-carbon-crankset-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-30mm-carbon-crankset-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Classified Powershift ecosystem adds direct mount crankset aero chainrings and more wide-range 12sp 13sp cassettes, carbon arms\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-30mm-carbon-crankset-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-30mm-carbon-crankset-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-30mm-carbon-crankset-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-30mm-carbon-crankset-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-30mm-carbon-crankset-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-30mm-carbon-crankset-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>lightweight carbon crankarms</li>\n\n\n\n<li>RaceFace Cinch Direct Mount chainring interface</li>\n\n\n\n<li>30mm alloy spindle</li>\n\n\n\n<li>170mm arms only</li>\n\n\n\n<li>146mm road or 154mm gravel Q-factor</li>\n\n\n\n<li>470g weight claim, 650g with a 50T chainring installed</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>1x Aero Chainring details</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Classified Powershift ecosystem adds direct mount crankset aero chainrings and more wide-range 12sp 13sp cassettes, Wolf Tooth chainring\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>1x-specific Drop Stop ST tooth profile chainrings, </li>\n\n\n\n<li>7075 alloy CNC-machined  by Wolf Tooth Components</li>\n\n\n\n<li>chainrings offered in 46, 48, 50, 52 &amp; 54T</li>\n\n\n\n<li>chainrings compatible with SRAM Flattop &amp; Shimano HG11 chains</li>\n\n\n\n<li>49.7mm chainline for the smaller ‘gravel’ 46 &amp; 48T rings </li>\n\n\n\n<li>45mm chainline for the larger ‘road’ 50-54T rings</li>\n\n\n\n<li>anodized black (bright purple is for pro athletes only)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>182g claimed weight (50T) </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>More cassettes, bigger 583% gearing range!</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_proprietary-system-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_proprietary-system-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Classified Powershift ecosystem adds direct mount crankset aero chainrings and more wide-range 12sp 13sp cassettes, proprietary\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_proprietary-system-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_proprietary-system-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_proprietary-system-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_proprietary-system-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_proprietary-system-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_proprietary-system-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>On the cassette front, more Classified cassette options is always a good thing, since their unique hub design locks users into their own proprietary cassettes. But Classified is doing a solid job of creating a lot more gearing options. The big news here is the addition of 3 different new 10-40T cassette options that combined with their 2-speed hub deliver a huge 583% gearing range, while also reducing gearing steps compared to conventional 1x setups.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another big benefit of moving to that 10-tooth is to get extra top-end speed on gravel &amp; mountain bikes that are limited to smaller chainrings due to frame clearance issues.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Classified Powershift ecosystem adds direct mount crankset aero chainrings and more wide-range 12sp 13sp cassettes\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new 583%10-40T cassettes come in three versions:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>12-speed gravel &amp; MTB for mechanical SRAM Eagle derailleurs<br /><em>275g claimed weight (10-12-14-16-18-20-22-25-28-32-36-40 gearing)</em></li>\n\n\n\n<li>12-speed T-type gravel &amp; MTB for electronic SRAM Transmission derailleurs &amp; flattop chains<br /><em>288g claimed weight (10-12-14-16-18-20-22-25-28-32-36-40 gearing)</em></li>\n\n\n\n<li>13-speed T-type gravel for the latest electronic SRAM Red Xplr derailleur &amp; flattop chain<br /><em>279g claimed weight (10-11-12-13-14-16-18-20-23-26-30-35-40 gearing)</em></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<p>There’s also a 4th new cassette, a 12-speed 10-35T for gravel but with tighter all-road-ready spacing. It still features a 525% range on par with the latest Eagle setup at a claimed 243g (<em>10-11-12-13-14-16-18-21-24-28-32-36 gearing</em>).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The trick to these new cassettes with a 10T small cog is they require Classified’s Powershift CD27 hub. So if you already have a Powershift setup, take a close look to confirm compatibility.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Classified Powershift crankset &amp; drivetrain additions – Pricing, availability &amp; options</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_new-kit-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_new-kit-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Classified Powershift ecosystem adds direct mount crankset aero chainrings and more wide-range 12sp 13sp cassettes, options\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_new-kit-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_new-kit-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_new-kit-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_new-kit-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_new-kit-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Classified-Powershift-ecosystem-adds-direct-mount-crankset-aero-chainrings-and-more-wide-range-12sp-13sp-cassettes_new-kit-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The complete new Classified 1x carbon crankset and chainring combo will set you back 450€.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Word is that all of these new cranks, rings &amp; cassettes are available now – although in limited numbers at first. The only exception is that you can’t get that bright purple Aero Chainring unless you get sponsored by Classified.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://classified-cycling.cc/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Classified-cycling.cc</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/classified-powershift-portfolio-adds-1x-cranks-chainrings-and-more/\">Classified 1x Crankset, Aero Chainrings &amp; More Cassettes Fill Out their Alt 2x Drivetrain</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"eb3007a3dc743510d840e75412afdf3584ecff80a64164ffcdea4bdb981007a9","category":"Cycling"}